(289, 'Me Kaci ne?', 'Kaci tana da abu ne da yake matukar salula don samarwa muku salula da ya dace, sauÆ™e shakka, sanar da matsaloli, kuma bukatar karin cikakken abin da za ku yi amfani da su. Kaci ta amfani da teknolijin masu zane-zane don bayyana bayanai da karin saÆ™o, kuma yanzu hanyar damuwa ga ra\'ayi ta hanyar mai karfi a matsayin taimako ga maÆ™otanci ta jama\'a.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 12:53:47', '2023-08-30 12:53:47'),
(290, 'Me kamar haka shine kungiyar da ke kasa cikin Kaci?', 'Kaci ta danganta da FactCheck Initiative. FactCheck Initiative (FCI) shi ne kungiyar tsayayyar baki daya a Nigeria wanda ake bada iyalan sa ga kaunar Æ™arfi, jinjiranci da siffanta maki, da amsa masa bayanai da kuma bayyana tallafin lamarin, hirar, matsayi ko kumallo akan birnin kasa da duniya. Kaci ta bar kungiyar da kasa, hanyar damuwa ga abubuwa hanyar kaunar Æ™arfi da masu nauyi mai kara da jinjiranci ta Æ™asar.\r\n\r\nKaci ta samu buÆ™atar damuwa daga wannan nasuwa, kuma bukatar yankakki mai karfi don tallafin yara dake cikin duk umurin gida.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 12:54:04', '2023-08-30 12:54:04'),
(291, 'Me sunan kayan abin da Kaci ta da?', 'Samar da sabuwar bayanai\r\nTsohon bayanai, Æ™asuwanci, Buzuwa\r\n\r\nRubuta bayanai\r\nTasin gidan wanzam, Ganin zaÉ“e, Bayyana tashin hankali\r\n\r\nRasewa bayanai\r\nRa\'ayin ra\'ayi, Sakamakon kayan bayani, Bayanin kula', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 12:54:33', '2023-08-30 12:54:33'),
(292, 'Me yake daga yake kan sanarwa na Kaci?', 'Muna ganin waÉ—anda suke rubutu a kan jerin mafarkin da suka fi so. Saboda idan jerin wasu karimci sun Æ™ammala a cikin Æ™asa, muna amince da su don damuwa tare da maÆ™on da suke Æ™ara, kuma saboda haka, mu duba su a jerin mafarkin da suka fi so.\r\n\r\nA bayan wannan abu da aka dubi su a cikin babu idanun wani abu mai dacewa, muna yi taimako da su musamman a damuwa. Jerin wasu karimci masu nauyi wanda ba a saba da sauri ba, an damu ta cikin jerin mafarkin da suka fi so.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 12:54:49', '2023-08-30 12:55:11'),
(293, 'Me yake aika jerin wakilci a Kaci?', 'Za ku iya sanya hotunan wakilci ta hanyar danna kika a cikin jerin wakilci a dandamali ko ku tura adireshin imel a cikin jerin wakilci a koÆ™arin shafinmu.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 12:55:42', '2023-08-30 12:55:42'),
