(305, 'Ta yaya Kaci ke samun labari?', 'Muna da tsarin da ke ba masu amfani damar shiga dandalinmu don aika labaran labarai iri-iri. Lokacin da waÉ—annan labaran suka mamaye yankinmu, mun sanya su cikin rukunan da suka haÉ—a da; labarai da ba a tabbatar ba, tabbatacce kuma tabbataccen labarai. Labaran da masu amfani ke bayarwa waÉ—anda ba a tantance sahihancinsu ba ana sanya su Æ™arÆ™ashin labarai marasa tabbaci.\r\n\r\nDa zarar Æ™ungiyar Kaci ta bincika don tabbatar da cewa labarin labarai a cikin kansa yana da wasu tushe na gaskiya ta hanyar tuntuÉ“ar masu ruwa da tsaki masu alaÆ™a, an matsa shi zuwa sashin da aka tabbatar.\r\nA Æ™arshe an Æ™aura labarin labarai zuwa matakin da aka tabbatar lokacin da aka yi kowane bincike mai yuwuwa kuma an sami martani daga masu ruwa da tsaki da abin ya shafa.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:06:51', '2023-08-30 13:06:51'),
