(327, 'Menene fasalin rahoton Kaci gabaÉ—aya ?', 'Kaci yana ba ku damar ba da rahoton wasu abubuwan da suka faru kai tsaye akan app kamar rashin da\'a na tilasta doka, ba da rahoton wani laifi ko yin Æ™arar da ya shafi app É—in. Kuna iya yin Æ™ara a cikin sauÆ™i ga hukumomin tsaro da suka dace ta buÉ—e app É—in Kaci kuma zaÉ“i zaÉ“in da ya dace.\r\n\r\nBabu iyaka ga adadin Æ™ararrakin da wani mai amfani zai iya yi. Koyaya, ana iya taÆ™aita korafe-korafen da ba a san sunansu ba saboda masu aikin na iya samun wahalar aiwatar da irin wannan korafin, idan ya cancanta, ana É“oye bayanai.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:14:38', '2023-08-30 13:14:38'),
