(334, 'Ta yaya zan iya ba da rahoton wani Laifi?', 'Kira lambar gaggawa kawai. Duk da haka, muna Æ™arfafa ku da ku yi amfani da Kaci a matsayin makoma ta Æ™arshe don irin waÉ—annan lokuta idan ba za ku iya isa ga hukumomin da suka dace ba saboda kowane dalili. Kaci ba aikace-aikacen tilasta doka ba ko tashar amsa gaggawa ba.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:16:53', '2023-08-30 13:16:53'),
(335, 'Zan iya ba da shawara ko yada ra\'ayi game da Gwamnati?', 'Ee. Kuna iya ba da shawarwari game da gwamnati kuma ku samar da mafita, muddin ba ta zama hari kan wasu mutane ko hukumomin gwamnati ba. Duk da\'awar dole ne a goyi bayan gaskiya.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:17:08', '2023-08-30 13:17:08'),
