(337, 'Zan iya ba da rahoton al\'amura ba tare da suna ba?', 'Ee. Lokacin da kuka ba da shawarwari ko bayar da hanyoyin magance matsalolin don gwamnati ta duba ko bayar da rahoto game da aiwatar da doka, muna kiyaye duk wani bayani da ya shafi sirrin ku kuma ba za mu kasance cikin haÉ—arin kama ku ba don bayyana ra\'ayoyinku masu dacewa.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:17:36', '2023-08-30 13:17:36'),
(338, 'Wane irin laifi zan iya ba da rahoto?', 'Duk wani laifi kamar yadda dokokin Tarayyar Najeriya suka bayyana ana iya bayar da rahoton ta hanyar amfani da Kaci App.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:17:47', '2023-08-30 13:17:47'),
