(340, 'Menene sabis na gaggawa na Kaci ke bayarwa?', 'Kaci yana ba da taimakon gaggawa ta yadda app É—in zai iya taimaka maka kai ga jami\'an tsaro, lambar gaggawa ko yin ajiyar motar asibiti idan an buÆ™ata. Lura, cewa Kaci ba aikace-aikacen amsa gaggawa ba ne kuma yakamata a yi amfani da shi azaman makoma ta Æ™arshe.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:18:10', '2023-08-30 13:18:10'),
