(343, 'Ta yaya zan yi ajiyar motar asibiti?', 'Da dannawa É—aya na maÉ“allin mun ba da damar zaÉ“i don kowa ya nemi motar asibiti ko sabis na kiwon lafiya na gaggawa kamar yadda ake buÆ™ata. Da zarar mai amfani ya nemi motar asibiti ta hanyar Kaci app, za mu kai ga abokin aikin cibiyar lafiya mafi kusa da ka zaba bisa ga halin yanzu kuma mu sanar da su bukatar ayyukansu.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:18:44', '2023-08-30 13:18:44'),
(344, 'Zan iya tuntuÉ“ar likita ta Kaci?', 'A\'a. Kaci ba zai iya tura ka kai tsaye ga likita ba. Kaci na iya, duk da haka, tuntuÉ“ar motar asibiti a gare ku daga cibiyar lafiya ta abokin tarayya.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:18:56', '2023-08-30 13:18:56'),
