(350, 'Ta yaya Kaci TravelSafe ke aiki?', 'Kaci app zai baka damar a matsayin matafiyi don saka wasu cikakkun bayanai tare da tsawon lokacin tafiya. Daga nan Kaci zai ci gaba ta hanyar tunatar da mai amfani don dubawa bayan tsawon tafiyar. Idan mai amfani bai bincika ba, Kaci zai aika da faÉ—akarwar SOS ga masu dogaro da bayanan da mai amfani ya bayar a cikin wasu don bin diddigin su.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:20:14', '2023-08-30 13:20:14'),
