(353, 'Shin jerin ayyukan gaggawa na Kaci zai iya dakatar da sauyin yanayi?', 'Idan kowa yana da alhakin tasirinsa ga muhalli, za mu iya dakatar da sauyin yanayi kawai. Dukkanmu muna da rawar da za mu taka, tun daga manyan kamfanoni a duniya zuwa daidaikun mutane. Kaci yana sauÆ™aÆ™a waÆ™a da rage hayaÆ™in CO2 daga ayyukan yau da kullun.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:20:51', '2023-08-30 13:20:51'),
(354, 'Wane tasiri mutum É—aya zai iya yi akan rage yawan amfani da CO2?', '2 na duniya ana danganta su da mafi arziki kashi 10% na yawan jama\'a (Oxfam, 2015). Mun haÉ“aka app É—in mu don tallafawa waÉ—anda ke da babban tasiri wajen wayar da kan jama\'a game da hayaÆ™i da rage su. Æ˜oÆ™arin yin aikin ku don muhalli yayin da mutanen da ba koyaushe suke raba damuwar ku ba na iya zama warewa da takaici.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:21:02', '2023-08-30 13:21:02'),
