(370, 'A matsayin abokin tarayya mene ne amfanin?', 'Fa\'idodi da yawa suna samuwa ga waÉ—anda suka yanke shawarar yin tarayya da mu. Bayyanawa ga kasuwancin ku yana É—aya daga cikin fa\'idodi masu yawa. Ana yanke wasu fa\'idodi da yarjejeniyoyin lokacin da muka tattauna bayan an same mu.', 'Hausa', '2023-08-30 13:24:24', '2023-08-30 13:24:24'),
(371, 'Maa ko min jin bayanin yanar gizo na Kaci tare da mutumin katin guda?', 'Eh. Maa ko min jin bayanin yanar gizo na Kaci tare da mutumin katin guda amma ba zai iya yi amfani da yadda ya taba iya yi aikin mutumin da kuma shara\'arun al\'umma\'i na Kaci.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 13:36:18', '2023-08-30 13:36:18'),
