(391, 'Yaya yana iya kawo jerin hankali na waÉ—anda suke da gidajen sarkin?', 'Eh. Zaku iya kawo jerin hankali na waÉ—anda suke da gidajen sarkin cikin sauran lokuna, kowanne daga cikin shafin Kaci kuma da ya samu damuwa da sauran hankalin al\'amurran.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 13:41:27', '2023-08-30 13:41:27'),
