(402, 'Me yana za ku iya binciken jerin Æ™arfinmu?', 'Æ˜unshin. In zaku iya so, zaku iya kawo jerin jerin Æ™arfinmu amma baki da kuma bincike na Æ™arfinmu kake a haka ba zai iya buÉ—e da dangantaka ba.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 13:43:53', '2023-08-30 13:43:53'),
