(410, 'Yaya yana iya yi amfani da sosai wajen Æ™irÆ™iri labarin da tafiya suke yi?', 'Tare da jiki na kwanaki na É—auki daga jerinmu za mu taimaka ta amfani da nau\'in damuwa don kiran anyi kyautar tafiya ko na\'urar nau\'in damuwa don kusan bincike ne da zai iya buÉ—e a matsayin damuwa. Bayan an soke wani damuwa ta kiran tafiya ta hanyar shafin Kaci, za mu tattaro asusun nau\'in damuwa na mafi gabanin ku wato wani nau\'in damuwa na É—aukaka da aka za a iya zaba a sauran jerin ku da muhimmanci na yadda ake buÉ—e masu amfani da shirin ku.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 13:45:52', '2023-08-30 13:45:52');
