(419, 'Me yana iya amfani da bayanan waÉ—annan nau\'in damuwa da Kaci TravelSafe?', 'Bayanan ku su iya ci gaba da kai wani nau\'in damuwa don damuwa, ba a iyali, kuma ba za a iya saitin damuwa don wata lafiya ko damuwa da nau\'wanku idan zata ga damuwa.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 13:47:58', '2023-08-30 13:47:58'),
(420, 'Me Kaci ta samu da rukuni masu sauki da dama tare da neman fuskantar kima a al\'amura?', 'Idan duk wani ke da abin da suke sauki a cikin nasara, zamu iya samun kyautar damuwa ta fuskantar kima. Mun gama kowane mutum ya samu karfi don yin damuwa, daga abokin zamani na duniya zuwa wurin É—aya. Kaci ta kara bukatar damuwa game da shirin domin Æ™irÆ™irar shakkaÉ—i da rikice-rakice na CO2 daga ayyukan ma\'aikataku.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 13:48:14', '2023-08-30 13:48:14'),
(421, 'Me yake son wani mutum ya Æ™i soyan damuwa ta CO2?', '49% na CO2 na duniya suna iya bada nasara zuwa masu zunzuru 10% da aka taimake su (Oxfam, 2015). Mu zama da kwanan wani jeri don taimaka wa masu damuwa wanda za a iya nuna É—ayan É—akunan CO2 da kuma rufewa. To, amincewa wa muku wani ayyukan damuwa don asusun al\'amura, idan kuwa suke É—auka masu wani abu game da damuwa.', 'Fula', '2023-08-30 13:48:28', '2023-08-30 13:48:28'),
