(509, 'Kedu ihe Kaci na-achá» na onye mmeká»?', 'Anyá»‹ na-atá»¥ anya ka ndá»‹ mmeká» anyá»‹ jigidere otu á»¥kpá»¥rá»¥ anyá»‹ na-akwado gá»¥nyere iguzosi ike n\'ezi ihe na nghá»ta ma gbasie mbá» ike na-ejere ndá»‹ mmadá»¥ ozi.', 'Igbo', '2023-08-30 14:16:13', '2023-08-30 14:16:13'),
(510, 'Dá»‹ ka onye mmeká» kedu uru á» bara?', 'á»Œtá»¥tá»¥ uru na-enweta ndá»‹ kpebiri iso anyá»‹ na-akpaká»rá»‹ta. Ngosipá»¥ta maka azá»¥mahá»‹a gá»‹ bá»¥ otu n\'ime á»tá»¥tá»¥ uru. A na-ekpebi uru na nkweká»rá»‹ta ndá»‹ á»zá» mgbe anyá»‹ na-ekwurá»‹ta mgbe anyá»‹ gachara.', 'Igbo', '2023-08-30 14:16:26', '2023-08-30 14:16:26'),
(511, 'Wetin be Kaci?', 'Kaci na online assistant wey dey run on autopilot to dey give you real-time tori, clear your doubt, report problem and request for service. Kaci dey use machine learning technology to give you information and dey ask for help on behalf of the person wey dey use am.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:29:22', '2023-08-31 03:29:22'),
(512, 'Which company dey behind Kaci?', 'FactCheck Initiative (FCI) na the company wey dey power Kaci. FCI na registered non-governmental organization for Nigeria wey dey focused on checking if tori dey correct, dey sensitize people and dey give solution to tackle tori wey dey mislead, fake news, stories, agenda or manifesto for Africa and the world.\r\n\r\nKaci come from this passion, and because people need to work with machine for life to dey easier.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:29:39', '2023-08-31 03:29:39'),
(513, 'Wetin Kaci get inside am?', 'Receive Tori \r\nInfoBank, Climate, Alerts\r\n\r\nShare Tori \r\nAmbulance, TravelSafe, SOS\r\n\r\nFollow Tori\r\niReport, Suggestion, Feedback', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:29:59', '2023-08-31 03:29:59'),
(514, 'How Kaci take dey get tori?', 'We get system wey allow users wey dey our platform to send us tori of all kinds. When this tori enter our domain, we categorize them as tori wey never dey confirmed, tori wey don dey confirmed, and tori wey we don confirm. Tori wey people send wey we never confirm e veracity, we go put am under tori wey never dey confirmed.\r\n\r\nOnce our Kaci team don check the tori well-well and we don confirm say the tori get truth for inside am by possibly contacting the people wey dey involved, we go move am go tori wey don dey confirmed. We go finally move the tori to tori wey don fully confirmed stage when we don check am well-well and we don get feedback from people wey dey involved.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:30:22', '2023-08-31 03:30:22'),
(515, 'How I fit register for Kaci App?', 'Just go online for the website make you follow the links wey dey there to download the Kaci app from Apple Store or Android Store and register.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:30:38', '2023-08-31 03:30:38'),
(516, 'I fit change my personal information?', 'You fit update your profile for Kaci; whether na your name, phone number, or emergency contact, you fit do all that inside Kaci.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:30:54', '2023-08-31 03:30:54'),
(517, 'How I fit logout from my account?', 'You fit just waka enter settings and logout from your account for the app. But, you no go fit enjoy the services and benefits wey Kaci dey offer you if you logout.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:31:09', '2023-08-31 03:31:09'),
(518, 'How I fit set up dependants for Kaci App?', 'After you don download the Mobile App and register, just click the part wey talk about dependants for your profile make you add dependants. You must add at least two dependants.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:31:27', '2023-08-31 03:31:27'),
(519, 'I fit open more than one account for Kaci?', 'We dey expect say every user go open just one account.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:31:40', '2023-08-31 03:31:40'),
(520, 'Wetin be Kaci Security Number (KSN)?', 'KSN na 10 digits wey dem go generate ONCE and ONLY when you don fully fill your profile details through edit profile and you don add the 2 dependants. E.g., 1000006712.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:31:53', '2023-08-31 03:31:53'),
(521, 'Wetin be Kaci reference number?', 'Reference Numbers, general reference numbers go auto generate for each module with KH, the first and last letters for each module and 10 digits numbers.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:32:05', '2023-08-31 03:32:05'),
(522, 'I fit share my Kaci activity results with third party?', 'Yes. You fit share your search results with third party as long as e no violate Kaci user terms and conditions.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:32:17', '2023-08-31 03:32:17'),
(523, 'I fit share my security/reference number with my family member?', 'For your own privacy and safety, e go better make you no share your reference or security number with anybody.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:32:30', '2023-08-31 03:32:30'),
(524, 'I fit change the language of Kaci App?', 'Yes, Kaci dey available for 11 different languages: English, Arabic, French, Fula, Spanish, Chinese, Igbo, Hausa, Portuguese, Yoruba and Pidgin.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:33:01', '2023-08-31 03:33:01'),
(525, 'How I fit turn off notifications from Kaci?', 'You fit turn off Kaci notifications through the settings for your mobile device for the list of apps wey get notifications.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:33:14', '2023-08-31 03:33:14'),
(526, 'Dem fit terminate my account anytime?', 'If your account violate our terms of use, we fit choose to terminate am anytime.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:33:25', '2023-08-31 03:33:25'),
(527, 'How I fit get alerts for tori wey dey trend and news?', 'To get alerts, just subscribe and register for the Kaci platform so dem fit notify you.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:33:38', '2023-08-31 03:33:38'),
(528, 'My data dey safe?', 'Yes. We dey take data security serious and we dey use the best encryption method to keep your data safe. Your personal information no go dey share with anybody wey no be Kaci and health or emergency officials if the need show face for you.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:33:50', '2023-08-31 03:33:50'),
(529, 'My data dey secure?', 'Kaci dey comply with industry standard for physical, environmental, and hosting controls.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:34:06', '2023-08-31 03:34:06'),
(530, 'Who dem dey share my data with?', 'To run the app and make sure say you fit enjoy all the benefits wey the app dey offer, we dey use services from different partners and providers wey go help us manage your data for us. For example, if you request SOS or Ambulance, we go share your location with the necessary officials or emergency contacts to make sure say you dey safe.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:34:20', '2023-08-31 03:34:20'),
(531, 'My data dey encrypted?', 'Yes. Your data no fit dey seen by any third party.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:34:31', '2023-08-31 03:34:31'),
(532, 'How dem dey use my data?', 'Kaci dey use your information inside the app and on need-to-use basis as per your request wey concern the services wey dey inside the app.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:34:47', '2023-08-31 03:34:47'),
(533, 'Dem dey use my data for other things apart from Kaci?', 'No. Kaci no go share your personal data with any third party apart from the agencies wey you choose or dem feature for your requests. We dey strictly follow the terms and conditions of our Privacy Policy and Cookies Policy.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:34:58', '2023-08-31 03:34:58'),
(534, 'Who I fit contact about my personal info for Kaci?', 'Just send us email for help@kaci.help', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:35:12', '2023-08-31 03:35:12'),
(535, 'Person fit use Kaci if e small?', 'Yes. You must dey at least 10 years old before you fit use Kaci.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:35:28', '2023-08-31 03:35:28'),
(536, 'Wetin Kaci report features dey about?', 'Kaci allow you report certain incidents directly for the app like if law enforcement dey do bad thing, report crime or make complaint about the app. You fit easily make complaint to the appropriate security authorities by opening the Kaci app and selecting the correct option.\r\n\r\nDem no put limit for the number of complaints wey one person fit make. But, anonymous complaints fit get restriction because operatives fit find am hard to act on top such complaint if the information no dey available.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:35:40', '2023-08-31 03:36:05'),
(537, 'How I fit report officer?', 'Officers wey dey oppress people, dey extort, or dey carry out any corrupt practice fit dey reported easily through the Kaci app at anytime without any form of restriction.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:36:24', '2023-08-31 03:36:24'),
(538, 'How I fit make complaint?', 'Just send us mail or call us with the details wey dey for the contact page.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:36:40', '2023-08-31 03:36:40'),
(539, 'How long dem go take resolve my complaint?', 'The time wey dem go take resolve your complaint (Turn Around Time - TAT) go depend on the reply from the target agency wey you select.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:36:53', '2023-08-31 03:36:53'),
(540, 'I fit make plenty reports or requests?', 'No dey limit the number of complaints wey you fit make.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:37:13', '2023-08-31 03:37:13'),
(541, 'Dem fit reject my petition?', 'Yes. If our team or target agency consider say e no follow our or their policy.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:37:26', '2023-08-31 03:37:26'),
(542, 'I fit withdraw the complaint or petition wey I don make?', 'E fit possible as long as the initial complaint or petition wey you make never go far.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:37:49', '2023-08-31 03:37:49'),
(543, 'How I fit report crime?', 'Just call the emergency contact. But, we advise say make you use Kaci as last option for that kind matter if you no fit reach the appropriate authorities for any reason. Kaci no be law enforcement app or emergency response channel.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:38:01', '2023-08-31 03:38:01'),
(544, 'I fit give suggestion or talk my mind about government?', 'Yes. You fit give suggestion about government and give solution, as long as e no attack any person or government agency. All claims must get backing with fact.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:38:13', '2023-08-31 03:38:13'),
(545, 'I fit report crime on behalf of person?', 'Yes, you fit, but you go need to give us certain contact details wey we fit forward to the authorities.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:38:25', '2023-08-31 03:38:25'),
(546, 'I fit report issues without showing my name?', 'Yes. When you give suggestions or solution to government for problem or make report about law enforcement, we go dey keep any information wey concern your identity confidential and you no go dey risk to arrest because you talk your mind.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:38:49', '2023-08-31 03:38:49'),
(547, 'Which kind crimes I fit report?', 'Any crime wey Federal laws of Nigeria talk, you fit report am using Kaci App.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:39:02', '2023-08-31 03:39:02'),
(548, 'Kaci fit solve my crime or petition wey I submit for platform?', 'No. Kaci dey in-between and no dey interfere for any case wey relate to law enforcement.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:39:16', '2023-08-31 03:39:16'),
(549, 'Wetin be the emergency services wey Kaci dey offer?', 'Kaci dey offer emergency assistance, so the app fit help you reach out to law enforcement, emergency contact, or book ambulance if you need am. But, Kaci no be emergency response app, so make you use am as last resort.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:39:28', '2023-08-31 03:39:28'),
(550, 'I fit make emergency call for night?', 'Our emergency service dey 24/7 because we always get people wey dey attend to you anytime.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:39:40', '2023-08-31 03:39:40'),
(551, 'If emergency show, I suppose make Kaci my first choice?', 'No. We advise say make Kaci na your last option because we no go fit carry blame if delay happen for response.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:39:51', '2023-08-31 03:39:51'),
(552, 'How I fit book ambulance?', 'With just one click, we don enable option wey anybody fit use to request for ambulance or emergency health service wey you need. Once you request for ambulance through Kaci app, we go reach out to the nearest health facility partner wey you select based on your location and inform them about the need for their service.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:40:06', '2023-08-31 03:40:06'),
(553, 'I fit contact doctor through Kaci?', 'No. Kaci no fit refer you direct to doctor. But Kaci fit contact ambulance for you from partner health center.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:40:20', '2023-08-31 03:40:20'),
(554, 'Kaci fit offer medical assistance?', 'No. Kaci app or chat bot no fit give medical advice.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:40:31', '2023-08-31 03:40:31'),
(555, 'How I fit give suggestion for Kaci services?', 'Just use the suggestion tab for the app or send us mail for info@kaci.help', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:40:44', '2023-08-31 03:40:44'),
(556, 'How Kaci fact-checking dey work?', 'We dey use automated Machine Learning algorithm to make this one easy.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:40:59', '2023-08-31 03:40:59'),
(557, 'Toris and stories wey dem share for Kaci, dem dey authentic?', 'We dey take time categorize every tori wey you see for Kaci. All the toris, stories or articles wey dey for Kaci dey categorized so you go sabi which one be gist wey dem never confirm and which one be true tori.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:41:14', '2023-08-31 03:41:14'),
(558, 'I fit submit stories and articles for Kaci?', 'Yes, you fit. Just send us mail using the details wey dey our contact page.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:41:28', '2023-08-31 03:41:28'),
(559, 'How Kaci TravelSafe take work?', 'Kaci app go allow you as traveler enter certain details including trip duration. Kaci go dey remind you to check-out after the trip don finish. If you no check-out, Kaci go send SOS alert to your dependants with the information wey you provide make them fit track you.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:41:42', '2023-08-31 03:41:42'),
(560, 'Kaci TravelSafe dey track my movement every time?', 'No, Kaci TravelSafe only dey track your movement when you enable the feature.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:41:54', '2023-08-31 03:41:54'),
(561, 'How Kaci TravelSafe dey use my information?', 'We go keep your information private and we no go share am with any third parties or partners, except for your dependants or emergency services if dem sense say you dey danger.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:42:07', '2023-08-31 03:42:07'),
(562, 'Kaci list of quick actions fit stop climate change?', 'If everybody take responsibility for how dem dey affect the environment, na so we fit stop climate change. All of us get role to play, from big companies to individual people. Kaci make am simple to track and reduce CO2 emissions from everyday activities.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:42:19', '2023-08-31 03:42:19'),
(563, 'Wetin one person fit do to reduce CO2 usage?', '49% of the world\'s CO2 emissions na from the richest 10% of the population (Oxfam, 2015). We develop our app to support those people wey get the biggest impact for raising awareness about emissions and reducing them. To dey try make impact for environment while the people around you no too dey show concern fit dey lonely and frustrating.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:42:31', '2023-08-31 03:42:31'),
(564, 'Wetin be Shop on Kaci?', 'For Kaci Shop, you fit find list of Projects wey you fit support, Merchandise wey you fit buy, and more.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:42:44', '2023-08-31 03:42:44'),
(565, 'Wetin shopping get to do with donor?', 'Buying Merch or Funding Projects fit make you qualify as Donor because the money wey dem generate from am go support Kaci\'s operations and Climate Change mitigation, respectively.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:42:56', '2023-08-31 03:42:56'),
(566, 'Wetin be Carbon Offset?', 'Offsetting go help reduce or remove emissions from the atmosphere so that dem go fit cover up for emissions wey people produce for other places.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:43:09', '2023-08-31 03:43:09'),
(567, 'Kaci work for both iOS and Android?', 'Yes. Kaci dey available for both IOS and Android platforms.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:43:21', '2023-08-31 03:43:21'),
(568, 'How much I go pay to use Kaci?', 'Kaci no get cost. You just need to download the app and register to use am.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:43:33', '2023-08-31 03:43:33'),
(569, 'I need to get subscription to use Kaci?', 'No. You no need subscription to use Kaci.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:43:46', '2023-08-31 03:43:46'),
(570, 'Why Kaci dey ask for donation?', 'As Kaci na free app to use, one of the ways wey Kaci developers fit improve the user experience na through donations. E go enable the developers to do more work to make the app better over time.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:43:58', '2023-08-31 03:43:58'),
(571, 'How I fit make donation for Kaci?', 'You fit use the donate tab for the app or visit the website donation page.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:44:09', '2023-08-31 03:44:09'),
(572, 'Wetin be the smallest amount I fit donate for Kaci?', 'There no be minimum amount wey you fit donate.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:44:21', '2023-08-31 03:44:21'),
(573, 'Wetin be the biggest amount I fit donate for Kaci?', 'There no be maximum amount wey you fit donate.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:44:32', '2023-08-31 03:44:32'),
(574, 'I fit collect my donation money back from Kaci?', 'No. The donation no dey refundable.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:44:45', '2023-08-31 03:44:45'),
(575, 'I fit promote my business for Kaci?', 'Yes, you fit.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:44:58', '2023-08-31 03:44:58'),
(576, 'How I fit promote my business or run ads for Kaci?', 'Just go our contact page make you reach out to us, and we go tell you how you fit advertise for Kaci.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:45:10', '2023-08-31 03:45:10'),
(577, 'My organization fit partner with Kaci?', 'We dey open to work with partners wey get similar values.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:45:21', '2023-08-31 03:45:21'),
(578, 'Wetin Kaci dey look for inside partner?', 'We expect say our partners suppose hold the same core values wey we dey stand for, including integrity and transparency, and dem suppose dey committed to serving people.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:45:31', '2023-08-31 03:45:31'),
(579, 'As partner, wetin I go gain?', 'Many benefits dey for those wey wan partner with us. Exposure for your business na one of the many benefits. Other benefits and agreements go dey discussed after you contact us.', 'Pidgin', '2023-08-31 03:45:43', '2023-08-31 03:45:43'),
