es\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Internet Explorer</a></li><li><a href=\"https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/enable-and-disable-cookies-website-preferences\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Mozilla Firefox</a></li><li><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/kb/PH21411\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Safari (Desktop)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201265\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Safari (Mobile)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.opera.com/help/tutorials/security/cookies/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Opera</a></li><li><a href=\"https://help.opera.com/en/latest/web-preferences/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Opera Mobile</a></li></ul><div><br></div><div>Bugu da kari, yawancin cibiyoyin sadarwar talla suna ba ku hanya don ficewa daga tallan da aka yi niyya. Idan kuna son samun Æ™arin bayani, da fatan za a ziyarci http://www.aboutads.info/choices/ ko http://www.youronlinechoices.com. Kuna iya fita ta danna nan: http://optout.aboutads.info/ ko http://optout.networkadvertising.org/ (ko kuma idan yana cikin Tarayyar Turai, ta danna nan: http://www.youronlinechoices. eu/). Da fatan za a lura wannan baya barin ku daga tallan da ake yi muku. Za ku ci gaba da karÉ“ar tallace-tallace na yau da kullun.</div><div><br></div><div>Muhimman kukis na gidan yanar gizon: Saboda waÉ—annan kukis É—in suna da matukar mahimmanci don isar da gidan yanar gizon ko app zuwa gare ku, ba za ku iya Æ™i su ba. Kuna iya toshe ko share su ta hanyar canza saitunan burauzan ku duk da haka, kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Me game da sauran fasahar bin diddigin, kamar tashoshin yanar gizo?</strong></div><div><br></div><div>Kukis ba shine kaÉ—ai hanya don gane ko waÆ™a da baÆ™i zuwa gidan yanar gizon ba. Muna amfani da fasahar software da ake kira share gifs (aka Web Beacons/Web Bugs), waÉ—anda ke taimaka mana ingantacciyar sarrafa Yanar Gizo da Sabis É—in KuÉ—i ta hanyar sanar da mu abin da ke cikin tasiri. Share gifs Æ™ananan zane ne tare da keÉ“aÉ“É“en mai ganowa, kama da aikin kukis, kuma ana amfani da su don bin diddigin motsin kan layi na masu amfani da Yanar gizo. Ya bambanta da kukis, waÉ—anda aka adana a kan rumbun kwamfutarka na mai amfani, gifs bayyanannu suna sawa a cikin shafukan yanar gizo ba tare da gani ba ko a cikin imel kuma sun kai girman lokacin a Æ™arshen wannan jumla. Muna amfani da bayyanannun gifs ko pixels a cikin imel na tushen HTML don sanar da mu waÉ—anne imel É—in masu karÉ“a suka buÉ—e. Wannan yana ba mu damar auna tasirin wasu hanyoyin sadarwa da tasirin kamfen É—in tallanmu. Muna É—aure bayanan da aka tattara ta bayyana gifs a cikin imel zuwa keÉ“aÉ“É“un bayanan abokan cinikinmu.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Kuna amfani da kukis na Flash ko Abubuwan Rabawar Gida?</strong></div><div><br></div><div>Adobe Flash Player (da makamantan aikace-aikacen) suna amfani da fasaha don tunawa da saituna, abubuwan da ake so da kuma amfani masu kama da kukis na burauza amma ana sarrafa waÉ—annan ta hanyar keÉ“ance daban-daban fiye da wanda mai binciken gidan yanar gizon ku ya samar. Wannan fasaha ta Æ™irÆ™ira abubuwan da aka adana a cikin gida waÉ—anda galibi ana kiran su \"Kukis na Flash.\" Kaci baya amfani da kukis na Flash. Koyaya, abokan cinikinmu na dandalin software na iya Æ™irÆ™irar shafuka akan dandalin Kaci waÉ—anda ke amfani da kukis na Adobe Flash. Kaci ba shi da damar ko sarrafa kukis É—in Flash na abokan cinikinmu, amma kuna iya samun damar kayan aikin sarrafa Flash É—inku daga gidan yanar gizon Adobe kai tsaye a nan.</div><div><br></div><div>Hakazalika, abokan cinikinmu na iya Æ™irÆ™irar shafuka ta amfani da Sabis É—in KuÉ—i na Kaci waÉ—anda ke amfani da fasaha daga kamfanoni masu amfani, kamar kukis da tashoshin yanar gizo. Amfani da waÉ—annan fasahohin ta abokan cinikinmu ba su rufe ta Manufofin Kuki ko Sanarwa 