don iyakance yadda ake amfani da kukis don dalilai na talla ta wasu É“angarorin uku masu shiga. Ana samun Æ™arin bayani akan waÉ—annan rukunin yanar gizon daga&nbsp;<a href=\"https://optout.networkadvertising.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Æ˜addamarwar Talla ta hanyar sadarwa&nbsp;</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://optout.aboutads.info/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Digital Advertising Alliance&nbsp;</a>, kuma ga masu amfani a cikin EU, Æ˜ungiyar Tallace-tallace ta&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youronlinechoices.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Turai Interactive Digital Advertising Alliance&nbsp;</a>. Har ila yau, Google yana ba masu amfani da yanar gizo tare da&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on&nbsp;</a>don hana tarin bayanai ta Google Analytics.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>11.&nbsp;&nbsp;A ina zan iya samun Æ™arin bayani game da kukis?</strong></div><div><br></div><div>Kuna iya Æ™arin koyo game da kukis ta ziyartar gidajen yanar gizo na É“angare na uku masu zuwa:</div><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.wikipedia.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">wikipedia.org</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.allaboutcookies.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">allaboutcookies.org</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.aboutcookies.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">aboutcookies.org</a></li></ul><div><br></div><div><strong>12.&nbsp;&nbsp;Tuntube mu</strong></div><div><br></div><div>Idan kuna da wasu tambayoyi ko sharhi game da wannan Manufar, ko kuma idan kuna son mu sabunta bayanin, muna da ku ko abubuwan da kuke so, da fatan za a yi imel: info@kaci.help.</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 05:27:30');
