(5, 'Pidgin', 'Cookies', '<div>Kaci Website and Mobile Application (wey dem dey call \"Kaci\", \"we\", \"our\" or \"us\"), dey use cookies and similar elements for their website for www.kaci.hep, Mobile App, to give the person wey dey operate the platforms (wey dem dey call \"you\", \"your\" or \"User\"), smooth, interactive and user-friendly experience. This policy go explain how we dey do am.</div><div><br></div><div>This Cookie Policy go explain how Kaci dey use cookies and similar technologies take recognize you anytime wey you use the app. E go explain wetin these technologies be and why we dey use dem, and also your rights to control how we dey use dem.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>1. Wetin be cookies?</strong></div><div><br></div><div>Cookie na small file wey dey carry set of characters wey dem send go your computer anytime wey you visit website. When you visit the site again, the cookie allow that site make e recognize your browser. Cookies fit store user preferences and other information.</div><div><br></div><div>Cookies dey provide convenience wey fit save you time, or e fit tell the Web server say you don return back to one specific page.</div><div><br></div><div>Cookies wey the website or app owner (for this case, na Kaci) set, dem dey call am \"first party cookies\". Cookies wey parties wey no be the website owner set, dem dey call am \"third party cookies\". Third party cookies fit allow third party features or functionality make dem dey available for the website (e.g., like advertising, interactive content and analytics). The parties wey set these third-party cookies fit recognize your computer anytime e visit the website wey dem dey talk about, and e still fit recognize am when e visit some other websites or apps.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>2. Why we dey use cookies?</strong></div><div><br></div><div>We dey use first party and third-party cookies for different reasons. Some cookies dey important for technical reasons to make our website or 