 more relevant to you. Dem dey do things like make sure say the same advert no dey always show, make sure say ads dey properly show for advertisers, and sometimes dem select adverts wey based on your interests.</div><div><br></div><div>v. Social networking cookies: These cookies dey used to allow you share pages and content wey you find interesting for our website, app or app and other websites or apps. Dem fit still use these cookies for advertising purposes.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>4. Third Party Tools wey fit dey our Website or Mobile Application</strong></div><div><br></div><div>We fit use and allow the following third parties to serve cookies wey fall into the categories wey we talk for top:</div><div>Google Analytics. We dey use Google Analytics service from Google LLC (1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043, USA) for the purpose of designing our websites based on your user preferences and to dey optimize these experiences. Dem dey create usage profiles wey no fit identify person and cookies dey used for this context. The information wey the cookies generate include:</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Type of operating system wey you use</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Browser type</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;URL (last Website wey you visit)</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Host name of the computer wey dey access (IP address - IP addresses dem dey cover so dem no go fit link am to any specific person)</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Time wey the server send request</div><div><br></div><div>You fit choose to no allow these cookies to install by configuring your browser settings so. E fit fit no allow you enjoy our website functionalities well. You fit prevent data wey dem generate from these cookies and your IP address from being processed by Google by downloading and installing browser add-on. You fit see more information about Google Analytics here. We dey use this tool only with your consent. You fit change your tracking settings anytime through our Cookie Settings.</div><div><br></div><div>5. How I fit control cookies?</div><div><br></div><div>You get the right to decide whether to accept or reject cookies. You fit use your cookie preferences by clicking on the appropriate opt-out links wey dem provide below.</div><div><br></div><div>You fit set or change your web browser settings to accept or reject cookies. If you choose to reject cookies, you still fit use our website but some parts of our website fit no dey available. As the way wey you fit reject cookies through your web browser settings dey vary from browser-to-browser, you fit visit your browser\'s help menu for more information.</div><div>You still fit follow the link below for more information.</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Google Chrome</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Internet Explorer</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mozilla Firefox</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Safari (Desktop)</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Safari (Mobile)</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Opera</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Opera Mobile</div><div><br></div><div>For addition, most advertising networks dey offer you way wey you fit use opt-out for targeted advertising. If you wan find more information, you fit visit http://www.aboutads.info/choices/ or http://www.youronlinechoices.com. You fit opt out by clicking here: http://optout.aboutads.info/ or http://optout.networkadvertising.org/ (or if you dey for European Union, by clicking here: http://www.youronlinechoices.eu/). E still dey important to note say this no go stop advertising from showing. You go still see generic advertisements.</div><div><br></div><div>Essential website cookies: As these cookies na strictly necessary to deliver the website or app to you, you no fit reject them. You fit block or delete them by changing your browser settings as we don talk for top.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>6. Wetin dey about other tracking technologies, like web beacons?</strong></div><div><br></div><div>Cookies no be the only way wey dem fit recognize or track visitors to website. We dey use software technology wey dem dey call clear gifs (also known as Web Beacons/Web Bugs), to take help us manage the Website and Subscription Service so we fit know which content dey effective. Clear gifs na tiny graphics wey get unique identifier, e dey function like cookies, and dem dey use am to track online movements of Web users. Different from cookies, wey dem dey store for user computer hard drive, clear gifs dey embedded invisibly for Web pages or inside emails and dem be like size of period wey dey end of this sentence. We dey use clear gifs or pixels for our HTML-based emails to let us know which emails dem don open. This one allow us know how effective some communications and marketing campaigns be. We dey tie the information wey clear gifs gather for emails to our customers\' Personal Information.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>7. You dey use Flash cookies or Local Shared Objects?</strong></div><div><br></div><div>The Adobe Flash Player (and similar applications) dey use technology wey dem fit use remember settings, preferences and usage similar to browser cookies but these ones dem manage am through different interface from the one wey your Web browser provide. This technology dey create objects wey dey store locally and dem often dey refer to am as \"Flash cookies.\" Kaci no dey use Flash cookies. However, our customers wey dey our software platform fit create pages for the Kaci platform wey go use Adobe Flash cookies. Kaci no get access or control over Flash cookies wey our customers use, but you fit access your Flash management tools from Adobe\'s web site directly here.</div><div><br></div><div>Similarly, our customers fit create pages using the Kaci Subscription Service wey fit use technology from tracking utility companies, like cookies and web beacons. The use of these technologies by our customers no dey covered by our Cookie Policy or Privacy Notice. We no get control over third party cookies or trackers wey our customers use.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>8. You dey serve targeted advertising?</strong></div><div><br></div><div>Third parties fit serve cookies for your computer or mobile device to serve advertising through our website or app. These companies fit use information about your visits to this and other websites or apps so dem fit provide relevant advertisements about goods and services wey you fit like. Dem fit also use technology wey fit measure how effective adverts dey. Dem fit use cookies or web beacons to collect information about your visits to this and other sites so dem go fit provide relevant advertisements about goods and services wey you fit like. The information wey dem collect through this process no fit allow us or dem identify your name, contact details or other personally identifying details unless you decide to give am.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>9. How often you go update this Cookie Policy?</strong></div><div><br></div><div>We fit update this Cookie Policy from time to time so e go fit reflect changes wey we dey make to the cookies wey we use or for other operational, legal or regulatory reasons. We go notify you about any major changes to this Cookie Policy before the changes take effect by posting the changes for this page and also by providing a more noticeable notice for the website or app or email notifications. E still dey important make you always come back read this Cookie Policy regularly so you go fit know wetin we dey use cookies and related technologies for.</div><div><br></div><div>The date wey dey top this Cookie Policy dey show when we update am last.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>10. DNT or Do Not Track</strong></div><div><br></div><div>DNT na concept wey international regulatory agencies like U.S. Federal Trade Commission (FTC), don dey promote am, for Internet industry to develop and implement one mechanism wey go allow Internet users control the tracking of their online activities across websites by using browser settings. The World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) don dey work with industry groups, Internet browsers, technology companies, and regulators so dem go develop DNT technology standard. As some progress don dey made, e still dey slow. No standard don dey adopt am to this date.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>Your mobile device settings</strong></div><div>Your mobile device fit get browser settings wey fit allow you manage the use of cookies, especially if the device dey support the installation of apps like iOS and Android devices. iOS and Android devices still include additional device settings wey control whether advertising partners fit use information about your app activity for advertising purposes. On iOS, you fit search for setting wey dem dey call Limit Ad Tracking. On Android, you fit search for setting wey dem dey call Opt out of Ads Personalization.</div><div>Third-party opt-outs</div><div>The major online advertising industry groups fit offer you way wey you fit use opt-out for targeted advertising by participating third parties. More information dey available for these sites from the Network Advertising Initiative, the Digital Advertising Alliance, and for people wey dey European Union, the European Interactive Digital Advertising Alliance. Still, Google dey provide web users with Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on wey go prevent the collection of data through Google Analytics.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>11. Where I fit find more information about cookies?</strong></div><div><br></div><div>You fit sabi more about cookies by visiting the following third-party websites:</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;wikipedia.org</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;allaboutcookies.org</div><div>â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;aboutcookies.org</div><div><br></div><div><strong>12. Contact us</strong></div><div><br></div><div>If you get any question or comment about this Policy, or if you go like make we update the information wey we get about you or your preferences, please send email to: info@kaci.help.</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 09:59:34'),
