(23, 'Pidgin', 'Terms', '<div><strong>1.1 Welcome to Kaci.</strong> Di following Terms of Use (wey dem go refer to as \"Terms of Use\" afta dis) na part of di agreement between you and Kaci App and WhatsApp/SMS Notification (wey we go call \"Kaci,\" \"we,\" \"our,\" or \"us\"), di people wey dey operate platform wey give you (wey we go refer to as \"you,\" \"your,\" or \"User\") access to our Mobile Application, WhatsApp/SMS Notification and any related services. Di Kaci Mobile Application and WhatsApp/SMS Notification get many waka waka wey include: TravelSafe, Ambulance, Climate, InfoBank, Suggestion, Feedback, SOS, Press Releases and plenty odas. Abeg note say di Kaci mobile application and notification no dey provide security services or ambulance services. If you wan take ambulance service, abeg ask medical professional or government agency wey dey responsible. If any emergency show, you suppose contact di emergency services for your country sharp sharp. Always dey ask your doctor or qualified health care provider if you get any question about medical issue. No use information wey you read from Kaci automated assistant replace doctor advice or cancel appointment with doctor. Kaci mobile application and notification fit use only information wey dem don give am and information wey dey online already take provide some information and services for you.</div><div><br></div><div>1.2 Dis privacy policy go explain to you di personal information wey we dey collect, how we dey use and share di information, and how you fit control how we dey use and share di information. E go tell you wetin Healthcare Professionals and oda members fit see when you dey use our Sites and Services. E go tell you your rights and choices wey concern your personal information and how you fit contact us if you get any question or something dey worry you.</div><div><br></div><div>1.3 Kaci dey run under FactCheck Initiative (FCI), wey be registered non-governmental development organization wey dem register for Nigeria with registration number CAC/IT/NO 130560. Dem dey focus on check say tori dey correct, dey sensitize pipo and dey provide solutions to fight misleading tori, stories, agendas or manifestos for Africa and di world.</div><div><br></div><div>1.4 If you wan holla us, abeg send mail go our Customer Service team for info@kaci.help.</div><div><br></div><div>1.5 You suppose don reach at least 10 years before you fit use di App. But if you dey below 13 years, you need consent from your guardian before you fit use Kaci and agree to these Terms of Use.</div><div><br></div><div>1.6 To fit use di complete power wey dey inside Kaci, you must agree say you go dey bound by these Terms of Use. If you no gree, you no fit use or access any part of di Kaci Automated assistant and mobile application.</div><div><br></div><div>1.7 Di language wey we go take arrange contract na English, but di Mobile Application dey available for 9 different languages wey be English, Arabic, French, Chinese, Fula, Igbo, Hausa, Portuguese, Yoruba, Pidgin and Spanish.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>2. Legal relationship between you and Kaci</strong></div><div><br></div><div>2.1 These Terms of Use dey cover how you fit use Kaci and e contain di terms wey dey control how you fit use di App. E dey important make you don read and understand di Terms of Use and our Privacy Policy before you begin use di App. If you no understand anything for these documents, abeg contact us for info@kaci.help, we go fit explain everything well well.</div><div><br></div><div>2.2 You fit only use Kaci if you agree to these Terms of Use. If you no gree with di Terms of Use, you no fit create User account for di app.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>3. Information wey we collect about you</strong></div><div><br></div><div>3.1 To protect your privacy and any data wey relate to you (wey we go call \"Personal Data\"), e dey very important to us. For dat reason, any Personal Data wey Kaci gather from your use, we go only collect am, store am and process am according to di relevant General Data Protection Regulations. Abeg read our Privacy Policy make you sabi how and why we dey collect and use your information so we fit give you di best possible service.</div><div><br></div><div>3.2 You dey give us right to use data wey we don anonymize according to data protection law. You dey accept say we go own any data wey we gather from di anonymized data.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>4. Kaci Services</strong></div><div><br></div><div>4.1 Kaci give you information wey go help you sabi wetin dey happun for news and confirm tori for internet. E dey use information wey don already dey available for public. Kaci Mobile Application fit also alert people wey you dey depend on (emergency contacts).</div><div><br></div><div>4.2 We dey provide Kaci for free through di App and WhatsApp/SMS.</div><div><br></div><div>4.3 Make you sabi say we dey provide Kaci just for information purposes. E no dey replace medical consultation.</div><div><br></div><div>4.4 Kaci no fit find information wey no dey already accessible online.</div><div><br></div><div>4.5 If you get medical issue wey relate to di information wey you enter for Kaci, na you suppose decide whether you wan see medical professional or seek medical advice.</div><div><br></div><div>4.6 Kaci no be weather app, betting app, and e no get power to predict anything.</div><div><br></div><div>4.7 Kaci Notification dey work on WhatsApp/SMS, e no dey work for Instagram, Facebook or any oda social media platform. Kaci no go fit work if you no get internet connection.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>5. Monthly Carbon Footprint usage</strong></div><div><br></div><div>E dey important make individuals contribute to help, and one of di ways wey you fit take achieve dis na by sabi how much carbon you dey contribute. You fit calculate your own carbon emission; dis na one of di benefits wey we dey offer. Through our app and partner websites, we dey provide platform wey no dey collect money to calculate your personal CO2. You fit set am to know your emission for daily, weekly, monthly and yearly. With simple question wey you go answer, you fit get correct result for your emission. Di exact formula wey we dey use na our secret, and e fit change or adapt anytime. As you sabi, wetin you dey do everyday, your food preference and oda habits na wetin go determine di result of di calculation. With all dis for mind, make you know and agree with di following:</div><div><br></div><div>a) Di result wey you go get, even though e go correct well well, e still go be estimate.</div><div>b) To calculate your exact specific carbon footprint fit no dey possible, so we no fit guarantee am.</div><div>c) Di carbon footprint calculator fit calculate wetin you go fit produce for future, but e no fit predict future. E go only give estimate based on di information wey you give.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>6. Creating User account</strong></div><div><br></div><div>6.1 Registration: You must finish di registration process by give di Company correct information like dem ask you for di registration form. For registration, you gree say you go provide correct, current, and complete information, and you go dey update</div><div><br></div><div>&nbsp;am anytime. You go choose username and password. Abeg no choose username and email address wey no follow rule or wey dey offend, or wey violate dis Agreement or any law wey dey apply.</div><div><br></div><div>6.2 Responsibility for Account: E dey your hand to make sure say your password and account dey secret. Plus, e dey your hand to make sure say no action wey you no know happen for your account. If you see say person use your account without your permission, abeg tell di Company sharp sharp.</div><div><br></div><div>6.3 Sharing: You fit share your Content with anybody you wan. If you decide say you wan share your Content, we go send person wey you wan give the Content instructions on how to see am. You sabi and gree say you decide who go see your Content and we no dey responsible for how person wey you give am take use am.</div><div><br></div><div>6.4 Liability for Account Misuse: Di Company no go fit blame if you lose something based on another pesin use your password or account, either with your permission or without. You fit also dey responsible if Company or another pesin get loss based on another pesin use your account or password.</div><div><br></div><div>6.5 Use of Other Accounts: You no fit use another person account unless di owner give you permission.</div><div><br></div><div>6.6 Risk: You gree say you go carry all di risk wey relate to your Content and any activity wey follow. Any action wey you do based on your Content, you go dey responsible for am. We no go dey responsible for your Content or any loss or damage wey happen as a result of how person take use your Content wey dey available for di Service. We no promise say your Content go dey available anytime you wan see am or we go keep am for specific time. You gree say you no get any remedy against us for any incomplete, wrong, or missing Content.</div><div><br></div><div>6.7 Account Security: The Company dey care for your personal information security. But we no fit guarantee say pesin wey no get permission fit use your personal information for bad purpose. You sabi say you provide your personal information at your own risk. You dey responsible to keep your information secret and to dey line with WhatsApp/SMS rules and privacy provisions. If you think say pesin misuse your User Account, abeg tell us quick quick for info@kaci.help.</div><div><br></div><div>6.8 How to register: Before you fit use the App, you need Apple ID or Google account. You fit download the App from Apple App Store or Google Play Store to your phone or tablet.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>7. Kaci Code</strong></div><div>Kaci Codes be series of numbers wey you fit collect as benefit from our partners wey dey company level, if you create user account after you download our app. Di Kaci Codes go increase di number of requests wey fit dey made for one day, one week, one month or any time period wey dem allot. Di Kaci Code wey you get go dey valid for di time wey dem allocate am and e no fit dey valid pass dat time.</div><div><br></div><div>Some of di terms wey you suppose follow when you dey use Kaci Code include;</div><div>a) You dey legally authorized to use di redemption as e dey within di terms of use of di redemption code.</div><div>b) You gree to di terms and conditions wey relate to di app and di redemption code and how to use am.</div><div>c) Di terms wey di specific corporation wey give you di Code fit apply based on di Kaci Code.</div><div>You fit contact di entity wey give you your Kaci Code if you wan know wetin dey inside am well well. You fit also holla our support team for assistance.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>8. Your right to use the Kaci Mobile Application and WhatsApp/SMS Notification</strong></div><div>8.1 Kaci and all di things wey dey inside am na our property or property of di people wey grant us di license (dis one still apply to third-party software wey dey for Kaci App). We give you right to use these things, but e fit only be for di purpose of using Kaci according to these Terms of Use.</div><div>8.2 We give you right to personally access and use Kaci. You no fit transfer dis right give another pesin, or sell, give away or transfer your User Account give another pesin. Your right to access Kaci no stop us from giving other pipo right to access am.</div><div>8.3 Your right to use di name \"Kaci\" or any trademarks, logos, domain names or any other kind of trademarks no fit pass wetin dey inside these Terms of Use.</div><div>8.4 As you comply with these Terms of Use, we give you small, non-transferable, non-sublicensable, personal, non-exclusive, revocable right to interact with Kaci for your device or to access di Website or di Screening Tool under di conditions wey dey inside these Terms of Use or di privacy policy, or under any terms wey apply to di App (WhatsApp/SMS or web browser) wey you dey use interact with Kaci.</div><div>8.5 As di User, unless e dey appropriately permitted according to these Terms of Use or according to necessary copyright law for di use of Kaci according to its purpose and/or necessary to get information wey go allow am work with other programs, you suppose no do di following:</div><div>a. You, as di User, gree say you no go copy Kaci, either as whole or part.</div><div>b. You, as di User, gree say you no go sell or make Kaci, either as whole or part, available give another pesin.</div><div>c. You, as di User, gree say you no go modify Kaci, either as whole or part, any way at all.</div><div>d. You, as di User, dey give assurance say you no go try find or access di source code of Kaci, either as whole or part, unless we expressly publish am and release am into public domain.</div><div>8.6 You sabi say we and/or di people wey grant us license for this fit claim any confidential information, rights of use, exploitation and recovery, plus any oda intellectual property rights wey dey fully or partially exist, regarding Kaci.</div><div>8.7 Feedback/surveys. If you give us feedback, ideas or suggestions, or if you answer surveys wey concern our Services (wey we go call \"Feedback\"), you sabi say di Feedback no dey secret and you give us worldwide, non-exclusive, irrevocable, perpetual, royalty-free and unlimited license to use your Feedback anyhow, for any purpose, and through any medium or technology wey dem know or wey dem no know, whether as whole or part, and whether as modified or not. We go always use your Feedback according to these Terms of Use, our Privacy Policy and any other law wey apply.</div><div><br></div><div><strong>9. Your use of the Kaci Mobile Application and WhatsApp/SMS Notification</strong></div><div>9.1 Apart from oda things wey dey these Terms of Use, this section ge