(32, 'Pidgin', 'Privacy', '<div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Website, Mobile Application (\"us\", \"our\", \"Kaci\", \"Kaci App\", or \"we\") and its affiliates dey value the privacy of individuals wey dey access our Sites and dey use our Services. E dey very important to us say we dey protect your data, privacy, and personal information. E dey very important to us say our customers (wey be \"users\") feel secure when dem dey use our products and services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This privacy policy (wey dem dey call \"Privacy Policy\"), together with our Terms &amp; Conditions, our Cookie Policy, and any other documents wey dem refer inside, e show the basis wey any personal data wey we collect from you, or wey you give us, go dey processed. Make you read this Privacy Policy carefully to understand the kind of data we dey collect from you, how we dey use am, the conditions under which we go share am with third parties, and your rights regarding your personal data.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">You fit use \"Kaci\" through our Mobile Application (wey dem dey call the \"App\"). This Privacy Policy dey explain how we go process your data when you use our App or wen you access our website wey be Kaci.help (wey dem dey call the \"Website\"), or any service and/or product wey we fit give you (Website together with the Mobile Application and any other product and services wey we fit provide, the \"Services\"). If some processing activities relate only to a specific product like the App or the Enterprise solution, e go dey clearly indicated.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>1. Who we be</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This Privacy Policy apply to any personal data wey Kaci or Factcheck Initiative process, wey be the data controller of all the activities wey dey involved with the Services wey dem offer for the Kaci Mobile Application, or the Kaci Website. If you get questions, comments, or requests about this Privacy Policy, make you contact us through our information desk at info@kaci.help.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This privacy policy explain the kind of personal information wey we dey collect, how we dey use and share that information, and the ways wey you fit control how we dey use and share that information. E inform you about wetin the Healthcare Professionals or any other member fit see wen you use our Sites and Services. E tell you about your rights and choices regarding your personal information, and how you fit contact us if you get questions or concerns.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">KACI MOBILE APPLICATION &amp; WEBSITE GO DEY COLLECT AND SEND PERSONAL, MEDICAL, AND HEALTH-RELATED INFORMATION ABOUT YOU. IF YOU USE THE APP AND OUR WEBSITE, YOU AGREE SAY WE FIT COLLECT AND USE YOUR PERSONAL AND OTHER INFORMATION AS WEY WE DESCRIBE INSIDE THIS SITE PRIVACY POLICY. IF YOU NO AGREE, ABEG NO USE THE APP AND OUR WEBSITE.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">YOU MUST BE 10 YEARS OR OLDER TO USE KACIâ€™S SERVICES.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>2. Important Definitions</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.1 \"Personal Information\" for this Privacy Policy, na information about you wey fit identify you personally, like your contact information (e.g. name, address, email address, or telephone number), personally identifiable health or medical information (\"Health Information\"), personal identification documents (like driverâ€™s license, voterâ€™s card etc.), and any other non-public information wey dey relate to that information.&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">\"De-Identified Information\" na information wey dem no dey use or wan use to personally identify one individual.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.2 Information wey We Collect or Receive from You</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a) Registration Data: When you register or create one account, you go give us some information, wey include your email address, telephone number, date of birth, gender, and zip or postal code (the \"Registration Data\"), plus password for your account.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b) Payment Information: If you choose to use fee-based Service like advertisement or make donation, we go ask you to provide (at least) your name and payment information wey include payment card information (\"Payment Information\"). Another service provider wey dey handle payments for us go collect your payment card information.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c) Information wey You Choose to Give Us: You get the power to give us different kinds of information during your interactions with us and the Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App, like the emails wey you fit send us, information wey you respond to, and the emails or newsletters wey you sign up to receive. Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App or third parties wey dey act on our behalf go collect data from you anytime you provide us with information.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d) Contact Information: If you choose to participate for research studies, or sign up for certain features, you fit provide us, and we fit collect, your contact information, like your name, mailing address, and phone number (\"Contact Information\").</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e) De-identified Data: We fit use de-identified data for research</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">&nbsp;and development of new products or tools, to refine our algorithms and machine learning applications, and to improve the App and the services wey we provide. We fit also share this kind of information publicly and to third parties, for example, in public reports about health, to partners under agreement with us, or in benchmarking information wey we give the medical community.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.3 Information wey We Receive from Third Parties</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a) Social Media Accounts: We fit collect Personal Information about you through the Mobile Application, or other third-party social media services like Facebook and Twitter, if you choose to link our Services with third-party social media accounts (\"Social Media Account\") either by: (i) providing your Social Media Account login information to us through the Services; or (ii) allowing us to access your Social Media Account, as e dey permitted under the terms and conditions wey govern your use of the respective Social Media Account.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">2.4 Information wey we collect using technology</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">a) Activity on the app, the automated assistant and our websites: We fit track some of the actions wey you take for the app, the automated assistant and our websites, like the searches wey you do through the Mobile Application or for the app, the automated assistant and our website.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">b) Access Device and Browser Information: When you access the app, the automated assistant and our website from one computer or another device, we fit collect anonymous information from that device, like your Internet protocol address, browser type, connection speed, and access times (together, \"Anonymous Information\").</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">c) Cookies: We fit use both session Cookies (wey expire when you close your web browser) and persistent Cookies to make the app, the automated assistant and our website and Services easy to use, to make our advertising better, and to protect you and Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App. You fit tell your browser, by changing the settings, to stop am from accepting Cookies or to prompt you before you accept a Cookie from the websites wey you dey visit. If you no accept Cookies, you no go fit stay logged into the app, the automated assistant, and our websites. We fit also use Pixels to make the app, the automated assistant and our website and Services easy to use and to make our advertising better, for example, by summarizing how people dey use am. For now, we no dey respect \"Do Not Track\" requests for all the parts of our Sites.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">d) Real Time Location: Certain features for the app, the automated assistant and our website dey use GPS technology to collect real-time information about the location of your device, so that the app, the automated assistant and our website fit connect you with a Security Agency, Healthcare Professional Services, or Ambulance service wey dey licensed or authorized to provide Services for the area or jurisdiction wey you dey. When you access Google Maps services for our Sites, e mean say you agree to Google\'s Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">e) Mobile Services: We fit collect non-personal information from your mobile device or computer. Dem generally use this information to help us give you the most relevant information. Examples of the kind of information wey dem fit collect and use include how you dey use the Kaci app, other applications, and the kind of device or computer wey you use. If our application(s) crash on your mobile device, we go receive information about your mobile device model, software version, and device carrier, so we fit identify and fix bugs and also improve the performance of our application(s).</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>3. How We Use the Information We Collect or Receive</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.1 Generally, Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App use the information wey we collect for the following purposes:</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To operate, provide, maintain, improve, and enhance our Services;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To understand and analyze how you use our Services and to develop new products, services, features, and functionality;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To personalize your experience on our Services, by providing tailored content. For example, we fit use your email address to help you create, log into, and manage your account for our Services. This one go allow us personalize your experience and give you relevant information. E still go make us give you features wey go help you understand, interact with, and track your health, and also give you personalized and relevant information;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For marketing and advertising purposes, like developing and providing promotional and advertising materials wey fit be relevant, valuable, or of interest to you. We fit use the information wey we learn about you to help us advertise our Services on third-party websites. If applicable law require am, we go only send you marketing communications if you give us your consent;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To communicate with you through email, text messages, push notifications, and phone calls, so we fit give you updates and other information wey concern our Services, give you information wey you request, respond to comments and questions, and provide customer support;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To facilitate transactions and payments;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To connect Social Media Accounts to our Services, to provide information from Social Media Accounts to your Profile. Depending on the Social Media Accounts wey you choose, and the privacy settings wey you set for those Social Media Accounts, we go access, make available, and store (if applicable and as e dey permitted by the social media service and authorized by you) the information for your Social Media Accounts so that e go dey available on and through your Profile for the Services;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For our business purposes, like audits, quality assurance, to find and prevent fraud, and to respond to issues wey relate to trust and safety wey fit come up;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For compliance purposes, like enforcing our Terms of Use or other legal rights, or as e fit dey required by applicable laws and regulations or as e fit dey requested by any judicial process or government agency;</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For other purposes wey we go provide specific notice for the time wey we collect the information; and</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">â€¢&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;To aggregate or otherwise de-identify information wey we collect through the Services, and use and share am for other business purposes after the data no fit easily link am to one identifiable person.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.2 De â€“ Identified Information</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">We fit use de-identified information without any restrictions.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">3.3 Information You Share with Third Parties.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This Privacy Policy apply only to the information wey we collect through our Sites and through email, text, and other electronic communications wey dem set through or in connection with our Sites. This Policy NO APPLY to the information wey dem collect by any third party. If you click on links for the app, the automated assistant, or our website, you fit leave our Site. We no dey responsible for the privacy practices of other sites, and we go advise you to read their privacy statements.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>4. How We Share the Personal Information We Collect</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App fit share or disclose Personal Information under the circumstances wey dem describe below.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.1 Affiliates: We fit disclose Personal Information to our affiliates or partners to provide the Services or for other purposes wey dem collect the information.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.2 Vendors and Service Providers: We fit share Personal Information wey we receive with vendors, relevant authority (emergency services or law enforcement upon your request), and service providers, for the provision of the Services and features of Kaci. If the Personal Information suppose be used for one different purpose from the purpose wey dem originally collect am or the purpose wey dem later authorize, or if</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">&nbsp;e suppose dey transferred to one third party wey dey act as data controller, Members go fit opt out (where practical and appropriate) of using or transferring non-sensitive Personal Information. For sensitive information, including health-related information, members go fit opt in before dem use or transfer am. For some cases, Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App fit keep other service providers to perform functions on our behalf, like website developers and IT services providers.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.3 Analytics Partners: We fit make some Personal Information available to third parties for analytics purposes, like: (a) for Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App business or marketing purposes, or (b) to use third-party tools to understand Membersâ€™ interests, habits, and usage patterns, and/or functionality wey dey available through our Services. We dey share your Personal Information with analytics partners to improve our own Services and/or to give you healthcare. We no dey sell your Personal Information to advertisers.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.4 As Required by Law and Similar Disclosures: We fit access, keep, and disclose Personal Information if we believe say na so we suppose do, to: (a) comply with any applicable law, regulation, legal process, or government requests, like court order or summons, or to cooperate with law enforcement or government agencies; (b) take measures to prevent liability; (c) protect your, our, or others\' rights, property, or safety; (d) investigate and defend ourselves against any third-party claims or allegations; and (e) protect the security or integrity of our Services and any facilities or equipment wey we dey use to provide our Services. For clarity, we fit disclose Personal Information if you post any objectionable content for or through our Services.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.5 Social Media Services: Our Services fit allow you to, based on your direction, share Personal Information with some social media services, like Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, and Google Plus. Abeg think well before you post content to any social media service, as e fit affect your privacy and anonymity. You understand and agree say the use of Personal Information by any social media services go dey subject to the privacy policies wey dey for those social media services and the settings wey you configure for their platforms. We dey encourage you to review their privacy policies.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.6 Marketing: We no dey rent, sell, or share Personal Information about you with companies wey no be our affiliates, for their own direct marketing purposes, unless we get your permission.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">4.7 Mergers, Sales, or Other Asset Transfers: We fit disclose and transfer Personal Information to service providers, advisors, potential transactional partners, or other third parties, as part of the consideration, negotiation, or completion of any corporate transaction wey involve say we dey acquired by another company, or we dey merge with another company, or we dey sell, liquidate, or transfer all or part of our assets.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>5. Security and Data Integrity</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.1 Data Security: Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App dey make reasonable efforts to protect Personal Information by using physical and electronic safeguards wey dem design to protect the integrity and security of the Personal Information wey we dey keep. We dey take reasonable precautions, considering the risks wey dey involved for the processing and the nature of the Personal Information, to protect am from loss, misuse, and unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction. However, as no electronic transmission or storage of Personal Information fit dey completely secure, we no fit guarantee the security or privacy of Personal Information.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">5.2 Data Integrity: We dey use the information wey we collect for ways wey dey relevant and compatible with the purpose wey we collect or provide the information for, as we explain for this policy. We go take steps to ensure say all information wey we collect, process, and/or store dey protected from destruction, corruption, or use in one way wey no dey consistent with our policies or the purpose wey we receive am for.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>6. Our Policy about Children</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Automated assistant &amp; App no allow registration or collection of personal information from anybody wey dey under 10 years. However, sensitive personal information wey relate to a child wey dey less than 18 years old fit only dey collected through one account wey an adult parent or guardian set up and dey manage. If we find out say we collect information from a child wey dey under 10 years, we go do everything wey dey necessary to remove that information from our servers. If you believe say we fit get any personal information from a child wey dey under 10, please contact our team at info@kaci.help.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>7. Information Retention</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">We take measures to keep your Personal Information for one period wey no go pass the time wey we need to achieve the purposes wey we outline for this Privacy Policy, unless the law require or permit us to keep am for longer. When we wan decide how long to keep am, we