ormation and other information for the purposes wey we outline inside this Privacy Policy. You consent to receiving text messages from us, including text messages with promotional content, even if you dey on the National Do Not Call Registry. You fit download the Kaci Privacy Policy in PDF format at: [Link to PDF](insert link to PDF here)</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>12. Governing Law</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">This Privacy Policy and any disputes wey relate to this Privacy Policy go dey governed by and interpreted in accordance with the laws wey dey for the Federal Republic of Nigeria.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Na the full Privacy Policy be this and e dey very important make you read and understand am well before you agree to use the Kaci App and Services. If you get any further questions or concerns about the Privacy Policy, you fit contact Kaci support for clarification.</div>', '2023-07-21 01:28:31', '2023-08-29 10:01:20');
