sp;É—o ne kala ngati cakkitii&nbsp;É—i am&nbsp;É—o ne.&nbsp;Æeen topÉ“e, ngamÉ—o e woppaama&nbsp;É“urÉ—eÉ“e, maa&nbsp;É“e nafoowo e e woppaama Network Advertising Initiative, e Digital Advertising Alliance, e yimÉ“e mum&nbsp;É—i ngamÉ—o kala jeyndu maa cakkitii&nbsp;É—i e yeewto mum&nbsp;É—i ngamÉ—o kala toon. Maa mbaÉ—i ngolli maa ngamÉ—o e woppaama: http://optout.aboutads.info/ walla http://optout.networkadvertising.org/ (walla so woni&nbsp;É—i ne kala Europe). Ko toon wonaa ko wonaa kala toon ngamÉ—o e maÉ“É“e kuÉ“É“al ngal kala maa.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>KukiiÉ—o duÉ—al ndi mum: Ko woni kukiiÉ—o&nbsp;É“ennunoo so woni ko e&nbsp;É“ennunoo janngoo&nbsp;É—i. Maa&nbsp;É“e jokkaa njogii en maaÉ“e&nbsp;É—i walla rokkondirÉ—e&nbsp;É“e kala toon, e kuÉ“É“al ngal.&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><strong>7. Gaynako ngam holle ngal yiÉ—de,&nbsp;É“een topÉ“e maayÉ“e, e mum kala jaÅ‹tol?</strong></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>KukiiÉ—o ngal haa daaÉ“ndeede jaÅ‹tol kala maa, e nde kuÉ“É“al ngal. Maa naatnoo e teknolooji ko â€œclear gifsâ€ (a.k.a. Web Beacons/Web Bugs),&nbsp;É“e maayi ne maaÉ“e ngal Websayto e Subscription Service ko woni e haali maa nde njeÉ—É—i&nbsp;É“eeÉ“e ko haa maa njogii. â€œClear gifsâ€ woppaama maa ngam&nbsp;É“een cakkitii, kadi eÉ“É“ini ngal mum, waÉ—de&nbsp;É“urÉ—i waÉ—deÉ—e. Maa maayi â€œclear gifsâ€ walla â€œpixelsâ€ e meeli HTML to maa woppaama&nbsp;É“urÉ—i e meeli&nbsp;É“urÉ—i kala walla e ngamÉ—o e-meeÉ—e. Maa naatnoo e â€œclear gifsâ€ maaÉ“e (yimÉ“e) e HTML maa yoÉ“re mum, kadi ko heege ko njiyaa to maa kuÉ“É“al kala meeliÉ—e mum.&nbsp;Æeen kala ngati maÉ“É“e â€œclear gifsâ€ walla pixels to kuÉ“É“al ngal maa e haali maa kuÉ“É“al ngal.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><strong>8. Maa woppaama yaamirde kala haa e Local Shared Objects?</strong></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Adobe Flash Player (kala suÉ“o ko waylo), natti ooÉ—oo e teknolooji walla heccinii kuÉ“É“al ngal ngam yiyde sabu kuÉ“É“al ngal, kadi&nbsp;É“een suÉ“É“e kala natti natti e toon ngam mum&nbsp;É—um naatnoo â€œFlash cookiesâ€. Kaci kokoowo e Flash cookies. Kadi, naatnoo ngam waÉ—de software ngal maa&nbsp;É“een ngam rokkondirÉ—e e Flash cookies mum ngam yiyde. Kaci kokoowo e Flash cookies. Tuma, ngal&nbsp;É—i ngam njoggoo e Flash cookies e ko faamde. Kadi, ngal&nbsp;É—i maayi ngam njoggoo ko ngamÉ—o kala toon.&nbsp;ÆurÉ—i woni, ngal&nbsp;É—i&nbsp;É“een ndiiÉ—o ndiiÉ—o kala natti natti, tuma yimÉ“e kala heccinii&nbsp;É“een ngam mum ngam kala juumre.&nbsp;ÆurÉ—i woni, kuÉ“É“al ngal toÉ“É“eÉ—e e kuÉ“É“al ngal naatnoo&nbsp;É“een toÉ“É“eÉ—eÉ—e&nbsp;É“een ngam rokkondirÉ—e.&nbsp;Æeen cakkitii kuÉ“É“al ngal maa&nbsp;É“e nafoowo to kuÉ“É“al ngal mum&nbsp;É—i.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><strong>9.&nbsp;Mi njogii yaamirde toÉ“É“ere e kukiiÉ—o maa?</strong></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Æuri fayde&nbsp;É—um, so woni kala toÉ“É“e kala maa. Ko mi&nbsp;É“een topÉ“e&nbsp;É—i&nbsp;É“ennunoo janngoo maa kala toon, ngamÉ—o e haali maa kuÉ“É“al ngal. Mi mbaÉ—i fuÃ±Ã±ude</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>&nbsp;e maa naatnoo&nbsp;É—i, kadi ko kadi mi ne cakkitii kala maÉ“É“e ngal, kuÉ“É“al ngal, cakkitii yimÉ“e ngal, kadi kuÉ“É“al ngal cakkitii&nbsp;É—i. Ko kala toÉ“É“e kala maa. Ko mi woppaama maa kuÉ“É“al ngal. Ko&nbsp;É“uri so woni kala toÉ“É“eÉ—e&nbsp;É“e kala maa&nbsp;É“een njogii so woni ko ngati toÉ“É“eÉ—e&nbsp;É“e waÉ—de.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><strong>10.&nbsp;Mi mbaÉ—i ngam holle ngal,&nbsp;É“een topÉ“e maayÉ“e, e maa kala jaÅ‹tol?</strong></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>So mi njogii&nbsp;É“een topÉ“e maayÉ“e e maa kala jaÅ‹tol, mi mbaÉ—i ngam holle ngal kala hakkunde maa e:</div><div>&nbsp;- Websayto maa e mum: [www.kaci.hep](https://www.kaci.hep)</div><div>&nbsp;- Kaci Mobile App&nbsp;É—i: Kaci</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Haa teeÅ‹tinnde kaÉ“irÉ—e maa, holluÉ“e maa haa teeÅ‹ti noon haa jeyÉ“e kala jeyaa e ngal&nbsp;É—i. Ko njaaÉ“É“udi kala waÉ—de kala ndeeÉ“e njaajo maa&nbsp;É—i. Kadi ko e hakkunde maa kuÉ“É“al ngal, maa mbaÉ—i holle ngal kala hakkunde maa kala jaÅ‹tol e