(50, 'Fula', 'Privacy', '<div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaci Website, Mobile Application (\"mu\", \"mu\", \"Kaci\" ko \"Kaci App\" ko \"muna\") da masu nauyi sun cika bayanai na mutane wadanda suka samu damuwa akan shafukunmu da suka amfani da su, don haka yanayin kukanmu, kuÉ—in da kuma bayanai na nau\'ukan gare ku shine dama mafi girma. Wannan shine wadannan masu nauyi a kan ku yana tunani cewa su masu nauyi (masu nauyi) suna yin damuwa amma su tunani amma su kama da shawarwarku don yin amfani da samfurinmu da layi.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Tarihi na yanayin ku (Tarihi na Layi), tare da shirar da Mu Terms &amp; Conditions, Mu Cookie Policy da kuma duk wasu abubuwa masu amfani. Ya tattaro asalin dukkan bayanai masu nauyi da muka samu daga ku, ko wani abu da kuke ganin mu, za a fita. Don Allah kar ku karanta wannan Tarihi na Layi tare da amfani da hanyar da ku sani dukkan abubuwan bayanai da muka samu daga ku, yadda muka amfani da su, sana\'ar da wani babu hanya daga masu nauyi biyu, da matsalar ku a kan bayanai masu nauyi.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Mun iya amfani da \"Kaci\" ta hanyar Mobile Application (shafin \"App\"). Wannan Tarihi na Layi ta bayyana yanayinku a matsayin damuwa lokacin da kuke amfani da App, ko don yin tsari ga shafinmu na yanayinmu Kaci.help (shafin \"Website\") ko wani layi da kake samu daga masu nauyi masu nauyi masu nauyi da kuma kayan aiki ko fasaha da muka ba ku (shafin tare da Mobile Application da kuma duk abubuwanmu na aiki, \"Services\"). Idan babu wani abu da ya tabbatar da bishiyoyin samfurinmu don wasu masu nauyi, kamar App ko yanayin bayanai na masu nauyi, wannan za ta tabbatar.</div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>1. Wane mu?</strong></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></div><div class=\"ql-align-justify\">Wannan Tarihi na Layi na Layi ya É—auki a cikin duk bayanai masu