on Allah a Æ™ara mu ta info@kaci.help. Mu so ku tambayi. Idan kun san yadda za a iya Æ™irÆ™irar Kaci domin zama mai rufe, duk wani tambayoyi game da aikinmu, don Allah ku tambayi mu a info@kaci.help.</div>', '2023-08-29 11:21:06', '2023-08-29 09:41:12');
